    # LOOKUP+GETATTR+OPEN+READ+RELEASE over the genuine fuse_in/fuse_out header
    # protocol across the real cdev and asserts the bytes == "FUSE-OK\n". No
    # disk needed. Prints "[FUSE] PASS ..." / "[fuse] PASS" at EMERG level.
