    # /etc/devmouse-write-test (planted by build_initramfs.py when
    # ENABLE_DEVMOUSE_WRITE_TEST=1, via scripts/test_devmouse_write.sh).
    # Same marker-scan shape as the gates above. devmouse_write_selftest()
    # (sys/src/9/port/devmouse.ad) injects "5 -3 1\n" via devmouse_write,
    # reads it back via devmouse_read, decodes the ASCII line, and asserts
